Date Time  API

Date, Calendar, SimpleDateFormat

 - Mutable
 - inbuild operations on date are not exhaustive
 - month - 0, year - 1900
 - 1970 jan-1


joda time API

LocalDate - represents date - ISO Date yyyy-MM-dd
LocalTime - time hh:mm:ss 
LocalDateTime - Represents Date and Time

Period - range between the dates
Duration - range between the time


ChronoUnit - DAYS,YEARS,HOURS

Temporal Adjusters
DateTimeFormatter - parse and formates the data and time



